org.jslipc.channel.buffer

Class ByteBufferQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractQueue<Byte>
        • org.jslipc.channel.buffer.ByteBufferQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Byte>, Collection<Byte>, Queue<Byte>

    public class ByteBufferQueue
extends AbstractQueue<Byte>
    A queue implementation that uses (a part of) a buffer for storing the queue elements and pointers. It is dedicated to be used with shared memory.
